        "Royalty modified in 11 instances in 2024.",
        "Program Fee cannot exceed current rate + 1% GRR over term. Funds reservation service, directories, advertising, QA, tech.",
        "Numerous additional distribution/sales fees: AAA ($0.30/room+10% commission), Consortia (up to $3.00/night+10%), TMC programs, US Government programs, ResMax (5.4%–5.9%), RMCC (varies by category), FastPay, Groups360, etc."
